data.description: I share with you an incredible home that truly stands out as a testament to the pride and joy of its current owner! The seller's dedication to upkeeping this home is evident, making it a truly remarkable property. This well-maintained residence is conveniently located near the community college and shopping centers. This beautiful home offers 3 Bedrooms and 1.5 Baths, but that's not all! Tile flooring and granite countertop updates provide a modern feeling. The driveway is generously sized, providing ample space for RV parking and more.  If you or someone you know is on the lookout for a home that combines comfort and functionality, this might be the perfect match! Book your showing today!
